<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { padding: 20px; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; }
        .header { background-color: #4a90e2; color: white; padding: 10px 20px; }
        .content { padding: 20px; background-color: #f9f9f9; }
        .footer { font-size: 12px; color: #777; margin-top: 20px; text-align: center; }
        .plan-details { background-color: #eef7ff; padding: 15px; border-left: 4px solid #4a90e2; margin: 15px 0; }
        .button { display: inline-block; background-color: #4a90e2; color: white; padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Your Nutritional Plan</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello {% if patient.name is defined %}{{ patient.email }}{% else %}Patient{% endif %},</p>
            
            <p>We're pleased to inform you that a new nutritional plan has been assigned to you.</p>
            
            <div class="plan-details">
                <h2>{{ plan.alimentRecommende }}</h2>
                {% if plan.description is defined and plan.description %}
                    <p>{{ plan.description }}</p>
                {% endif %}
                
                <p>Dear {{ patient.name }},</p>
                <p>Your nutritional plan has been assigned. Please find the details in the attached PDF.</p>
                <p>Best regards,</p>
                <p>Your Medical Team</p>
            
            <p>Please log in to your patient portal to view the complete details of your plan, including daily meal recommendations and nutritional guidelines.</p>
            
            <p>If you have any questions about your plan, please contact your nutritionist.</p>
            
            <p>Best regards,<br>
            Your Healthcare Team</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
     
            <p>Â©  Your Nutrition Center. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>